<br />
Constitutions returns for all classes are so dismal it hides the high cost on +hp stats.<br />
<br />
Hopefully in the future we dont see items with +100hp/energy because it will just kill the &quot;value&quot; of said item into worthlessness, especially when compared to having +12 int/+12 wis instead.
                  
